</P>
<P>
 Kochsmeier, Wayne H., 64, of North Hills, electronics technician for Sony 
Corp. Utter-McKinley Mortuary, Mission Hills. 
</P>
<P>
 La Due, Donn, 71, of Van Nuys, retired technician for Deluxe Laboratories. 
Pierce Brothers Valhalla Mortuary, North Hollywood. 
</P>
<P>
 Lopatoff, Mitchell, 71, of Lancaster, retired aerospace engineer. Murphy 
Mortuary, Lancaster. 
</P>
<P>
 Monroe, Mary Lou, 75, of Van Nuys, retired first aid instructor for the 
American Red Cross. Aftercare California Cremation & Burial Society, Van Nuys. 
</P>
<P>
 Papazian, Margareta, 67, of North Hollywood, clerk for Organically Grown. 
Forest Lawn Mortuary, Hollywood Hills. 
</P>
<P>
