Buena (7-0, 7-0 in league meets), which snapped Rio Mesa's string of league 
titles at eight. Meaghan Dunne won the 800 in 2 minutes 22.7 seconds for Buena, 
which tied Rio Mesa for the league title in 1987. 
</P>
