diversified high technology company.Washington, who joined Rockwell in 1969, 
had been vice president for business development. Before that, he was vice 
president for strategic management at Rockwell's Defense Electronics business 
in Anaheim. Washington also served as vice president and general manager of 
Rockwell's Autonetics Marine Systems division from 1988 to 1990. 
</P>
</TEXT>
