 Joe Magrane, who's scheduled to rejoin the pitching rotation by May 6, yielded 
five hits and an earned run in six innings Wednesday night in his second 
rehabilitative assignment for Class-A Lake Elsinore. He threw 62 strikes in 84 
pitches. BOB NIGHTENGALE 
