<TEXT>
<P>
 Microsemi Corp. said Thursday that it has agreed to form a joint venture in 
China with Shanghai Electrical Apparatus Corp. to manufacture semiconductor 
products. 
</P>
<P>
 Microsemi, based in Santa Ana, will own 60% of the joint venture, which will 
be near Shanghai Electrical's plant in Shanghai. The manufacturing plant is 
scheduled to be completed in a year. 
</P>
