<TEXT>
<P>
 Cal State Fullerton has signed six players for its women's soccer program. 
</P>
<P>
 The group includes incoming freshmen Krista Broughton of Canyon High School, 
Kimberly McKay of Capistrano Valley and Erin Rico of Norco High School. 
</P>
<P>
 Other soccer recruits include Debbie Klein of Huntington Beach and Caren 
Morgan of Whittier. Both played last season for Cypress College. The other 
addition is Jennifer Bryant of Yorba Linda, who is transferring from Cal Poly 
Pomona. 
